															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1372582); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1372582&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610252631" alt="Jacob Conwell" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1372582)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1372582); return false;" >Jacob Conwell</a></span> <span class="odate time_1456171476 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">22 Feb 2016 20:04</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2461462">
									

<p>And with this tale, I'm pleased to introduce MTF Eta-13 (Gulliver's Tourists) for the 2016 MTF Contest. This is set to be the first part of a four piece series starring this Task Force.</p>
<p>Special thanks to my teammates DreamwalkerFae and kol aumer for their assistance creating the characters and setting.</p>
<p>Additional thanks to Dr.Leonard, TwistedGears, and Crayne for their feedback when this was a draft.</p>
<p>Enjoy the tale.</p>

