						<a class="title" href="javascript:;" onclick="togglePostFold(event,2461462)">Author&#039;s Post</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1372582); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1372582&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610252631" alt="Jacob Conwell" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1372582)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1372582); return false;" >Jacob Conwell</a></span>, <span class="odate time_1456171476 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">22 Feb 2016 20:04</span>
